                                                                      LinkedHashMap<String,AbstractHttpField> fields,

It returns the AbstractHttpBusinessRequest to use during a new request. Note that fields given in parameter should be updated according to their values if needed.

Parameters:
remoteAddress - the remote SocketAddress in use
fields - the fields linked hashmap (to preserver order) to set for the new request
page - source HttpPage
Returns:
